<item>
            <title>[LU-7263] object leak in mdt_reint_rename_internal()</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7263</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In &lt;tt&gt;mdt_reint_rename_internal()&lt;/tt&gt; if the &lt;tt&gt;mnew&lt;/tt&gt; object is remote then it gets leaked. The last goto label below should be &lt;tt&gt;out_put_new&lt;/tt&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;                &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (!fid_is_md_operative(new_fid))
                        GOTO(out_put_old, rc = -EPERM);

                mnew = mdt_object_find(info-&amp;gt;mti_env, info-&amp;gt;mti_mdt, new_fid);
                &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (IS_ERR(mnew))
                        GOTO(out_put_old, rc = PTR_ERR(mnew));

                &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (mdt_object_remote(mnew)) {
                        struct mdt_body  *repbody;

                        &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;/* Always send rename req to the target child MDT */&lt;/span&gt;
                        repbody = req_capsule_server_get(info-&amp;gt;mti_pill,
                                                         &amp;amp;RMF_MDT_BODY);
                        LASSERT(repbody != NULL);
                        repbody-&amp;gt;mbo_fid1 = *new_fid;
                        repbody-&amp;gt;mbo_valid |= (OBD_MD_FLID | OBD_MD_MDS);
                        GOTO(out_put_old, rc = -EXDEV);
                }
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This leak is reachable.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
